OL,3,CViolence against women and girls 'the
OL,4,Cpriority': new Cumbria Chief Constable
OL,6,FCumbria Police's newly appointed Chief
OL,7,FConstable has said his top priority in
OL,8,Fthe role will be to tackle the rising
OL,9,Freports of violence against women and
OL,10,Fgirls.
OL,12,FAfter acting as temporary chief
OL,13,Fconstable, Martland was appointed
OL,14,Funanimously to the permanent role by
OL,15,FCumbria's police, fire and crime panel.
OL,17,FIn an interview with ITV Border, Chief
OL,18,FConstable Martland outlined the areas
OL,19,Fon which he wants to focus.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
