PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1772572325
OL,3,CViolence against women and girls 'the
OL,4,Cpriority': new Cumbria Chief Constable
OL,6,FThe possibility of Cumbria
OL,7,FConstabulary being disbanded to make
OL,8,Fway for a regional police force, as
OL,9,FHome Secretary Shabana Mahmood MP has
OL,10,Fmooted, was criticised by Martland.
OL,12,FWhen asked whether he agreed with the
OL,13,Fproposals, he said: "The simple answer
OL,14,Fis 'no'.
OL,16,F"We are an organisation that is
OL,17,Fperforming really well. In terms of
OL,18,Fthe (national crime) survey recently,
OL,19,Fout of seven measures of confidence,
OL,20,Fwe are number one in the country for
OL,21,Ffive out of seven.
OL,26,@zD@EpmzD@Tpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
