PN,35407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1772572325
OL,3,CViolence against women and girls 'the
OL,4,Cpriority': new Cumbria Chief Constable
OL,6,F"I accept there is a need for reform
OL,7,Fof policing. There are certain things
OL,8,Fthat we need to advance, need to do
OL,9,Fbetter: use of technology, a more
OL,10,Fjoined up strategic approach.
OL,12,F"My job here is to keep the people of
OL,13,FCumbria safe today and in the future.
OL,14,FI want to focus here, keeping the
OL,15,Fpeople of Cumbria safe today and in
OL,16,Fthe future."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
